{"id": "art-264", "label": "Art. 264", "title": "Art. 264", "slug": "art-264", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 264 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Numirea\nlichidatorilor în <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> pe <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în\ncomandit&#259; pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> se face de adunarea\ngeneral&#259;, care <span class=SpellE>hot&#259;r&#259;&#351;te</span>\nlichidarea, dac&#259;, prin actul constitutiv, nu se prevede altfel.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Adunarea general&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>hot&#259;r&#259;&#351;te</span> cu majoritatea prev&#259;zut&#259;\npentru modificarea actului constitutiv.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_715003067\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1135\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_715003067\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul în care majoritatea nu a fost <span\nclass=SpellE>ob&#355;inut&#259;</span>, numirea se face de tribunal, la cererea\noric&#259;ruia dintre administratori, respectiv dintre membrii directoratului,\nsau dintre <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>, cu citarea <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a\ncelor care au cerut-o. Hot&#259;rârea este supus&#259; numai apelului.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}